Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,侵入秋葉原集群的偷渡屋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,與巡視員交火後目前仍然在逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,萬世橋為慶祝發放烤肉便當 領取的群眾排隊成長龍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,偷渡屋的破壞引發的森林火災依然持續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,受災的低保群眾發動遊行要求改善待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還有多數博物館遭劫掠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,任關八州聯合會長的黑道頭目 侃王八百八氏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,發表了批評偷渡屋的言論
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他說他們是唆使模範黑道違背俠義之道的異端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,據奮戰中的無人機巡視員同志報告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,卑劣的偷渡屋依然在逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因偷渡屋的暴亂 東部商廈破環嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因偷渡屋的槍擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因偷渡屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易到了三軒茶屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,店全都關了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,明明有好多美食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,戒嚴令就是因為我們發的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 目標的端末呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是傳說中的端末
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,對 是公共電話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然聽說過 沒想到在這個地方藏著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,現在多數線路已被切斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想聯絡M只能靠這部電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是最後的希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,龜速線路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微費點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,連線結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了M的回信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,內容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,只有文本和垃圾文件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,蜥蜴斷尾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這回復好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,接受現實吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就算拋棄我們 M的措辭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也不會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看附件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,無意義的音訊檔案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就算聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,播放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,單純的雜音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有嵌入代碼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,此處不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這個節奏是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是舞曲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿呦呦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿呦呦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,聽 聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是開溜舞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,M說 他想逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界的管理者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對 不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼那麼肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是我想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這是和M定好的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能會錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會真打算幫他逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,先撤離吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,走後門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去要筋疲力盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒子彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,現在只能逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不能丟下你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想在這同歸於盡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,世上無論何事都需要覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,偷渡屋 黑道 魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持不可讓步的原則
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,為此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,阿卡姆 阿卡姆 蒂林哈斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,獨白朗讀匯於一發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一發乾掉那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一發 一發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一發？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一髮屋 十一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法少女十一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,前來華麗助戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡暫時是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,讓菲利斯好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 十一先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 你真是那個頭頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了 馬爾提
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,小姑娘 要懂得點到為止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,三軒茶屋的仲裁者也是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道是藏不下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.56,Top,,0,0,0,,給我個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我能幫你的只有食物和彈藥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,還有稍微帶帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,之後怎麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.76,Top,,0,0,0,,什麼東西 真難喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你就告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有人告訴我想要逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不得不逃的是艾庫亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所言極是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,身為黑道說想成為魔法少女時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞也沒有嘲笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,還說支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因為偷渡屋的一句話我便得到了救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,十一先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,說笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只是突然想說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞的心情是真心實意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,逃出路線定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,走西門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要去東門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐 那不是市中的方向嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊就是大橋集群了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,全是病人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,處理傷口就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,途徑大橋集群
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再經過澀谷和青山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是大江戶城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大江戶城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,說真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是管理員坐鎮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,M正向我們求助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不能坐視不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是聽說大江戶城是警備最森嚴的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此 也不能放棄委託人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看清形勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才都那麼狼狽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就這還想衝進大江戶城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這是去自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒打算自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,失去了絕地之幸還能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,被流彈擊中就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有自信能保護好你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,恕不奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣去很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這與赤膊上陣無異
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 不會連累菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做的只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,承蒙照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣真的不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼不滿就快點說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是對你不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是阿汪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞學姐 我看不慣這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒挽留菲利斯學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼 這樣太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然她不在了我就能獨占艾庫亞學姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,和馬爾提一樣喜歡學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然而這是什麼態度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就那麼從容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我也不知如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我終於找到了一個學姐的缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,無論說什麼都不會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,對對方完全沒興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,對對方不抱任何期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,對我也是 對她也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果馬爾提說要退出的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就像剛才那樣表示理解然後辭別嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那我該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來 為了我跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你對我是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能依靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她剛才肯定在等這句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,然而艾庫亞學姐哪怕說了一句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 要是馬爾提的話肯定會跪地嚎啕大哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,硬撐著的菲利斯學姐肯定很失落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾提的不滿就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好結束 這個話題到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要放棄攻城嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是破天荒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 話說你輕點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 請跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 剛才怎麼沒挽留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我走神了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,走神了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因為擔心你的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但我還是不願這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很危險 但是請跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,幫幫我吧 協助我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我很困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,困擾也要來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,最初就該這麼強硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 這多虧了馬爾提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 回到大家那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 那個史萊姆怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我好在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,說明一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,您先請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,總之潛入進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不歸隊也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,還是要謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 還差一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,直到最後請各位多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題 艾庫亞學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不至於 抬起頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,開衝吧 領導
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,請稍等 M
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對幫你逃走
